'''''Life of Kylie''''' (''LOK'') is an American [[reality television]] series starring [[Kylie Jenner]]. The eight-part half-hour series premiered on August 6, 2017, on the [[E!]] cable network.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cosmopolitan.com/entertainment/tv/a10016743/life-of-kylie-new-trailer/|title=New ''Life of Kylie'' Trailer Confirms Kylie Jenner's Hiccups Are Hilarious|work=[[Cosmopolitan (magazine)|Cosmopolitan]]|accessdate=June 14, 2017|date=June 13, 2017|first=Eliza|last=Thompson}}</ref> The reality series was [[greenlight|greenlit]] on April 10, 2017.<ref>{{cite press|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2017/04/10/19-year-old-cosmetics-mogul-and-social-media-powerhouse-kylie-jenner-set-to-star-and-executive-produce-new-e-docuseries-life-of-kylie-494204/20170410e01/|title=19-Year-Old Cosmetics Mogul and Social Media Powerhouse Kylie Jenner Set to Star and Executive Produce New E! Docuseries "Life of Kylie"|work=[[The Futon Critic]]|date=April 10, 2017|accessdate=April 11, 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/tv/ct-kylie-jenner-gets-tv-show-20170410-story.html|title=Kylie Jenner getting reality TV show called 'Life of Kylie'|accessdate=April 11, 2017|work=[[Chicago Tribune]]|date=April 10, 2017}}</ref> On May 11, 2017, [[E!]] released the first promo video of the series.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eonline.com/shows/life_of_kylie/news/850269/watch-the-first-look-at-kylie-jenner-s-new-e-series-life-of-kylie|title=Watch the First Look at Kylie Jenner's New E! Series Life of Kylie!|work=[[E! News]]|date=May 11, 2017|accessdate=August 13, 2017|first=Brett|last=Malec}}</ref> This series ended on September 17, 2017.

== Premise ==
The series follows the life of fashion entrepreneur and reality television personality [[Kylie Jenner]] as she deals with running a business while maintaining a normal life and her close friendship with Jordyn Woods. In a statement about getting her own series, Jenner notes, "The last couple years have been such an incredible journey with the support of my fans," also adding, "This show will allow me to give them a peek inside all of the exciting things I am working on as well as some personal time with friends."<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2017/tv/news/kylie-jenner-spinoff-life-of-kylie-e-1202027408/|title=Kylie Jenner Spinoff Series ‘Life of Kylie’ Gets Greenlight at E!|work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|first=Joe|last=Otterson|date=April 10, 2017|accessdate=April 11, 2017}}</ref>

